{"tid":253962,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人有去過希臘？","createTime":"2017-05-22T20:16:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-23T20:45:22.000Z","uid":87158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4175de8b68d994c333e5532263372c5a1c4dfb0b","tid":253962,"uid":87158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T20:16:54.000Z","msg":"小弟就想八月自己去窮遊希臘自由行8日<br />\n先講大約行程(因為係自己一個男仔所以行程比較chur 也無所謂。)<br />\nDay 1-2Athens <br />\nDay3 Meteora (即日來回Athens)<br />\nDay 4Mystra（即日來回Athens）<br />\nDay 5-6 Santorini(第5日坐船去）<br />\nDay 7 Iraklion <br />\nDay 8 返去Athens<br />\n其次就幾個問題想問下有去過希臘嘅巴打<br />\n<br />\n第一個係我預算16000港元（不包機票），請問足唔足夠？當地大約洗費太約約多？我主要參觀多<br />\n<br />\n第二個就想問大家仲有冇咩地方可以推薦和行程有冇咩大問題，有咩地方應該花更多時間去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第三個另外如果由第一日開始就去Santorini,最後先去Athens，會不會比較好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01157b8008ed12d9844e08304976f8798e86a777","tid":253962,"uid":47565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T23:33:03.000Z","msg":"Meteroa要即日來回一定要坐火車<br />\n但前提佢無罷工<br />\n<br />\n另外個plan唔係唔得<br />\n不過就有啲趕頭趕命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecd08c317106cdc6c6913494f2700292d78511b9","tid":253962,"uid":3581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T00:01:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Meteroa要即日來回一定要坐火車<br />\n但前提佢無罷工<br />\n<br />\n另外個plan唔係唔得<br />\n不過就有啲趕頭趕命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正常計埋飛機來回要幾多日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94287ddd82e24b0fd8b7f88760c16f47459a37ae","tid":253962,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T00:32:33.000Z","msg":"meteora你即日來回可以睇咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一程都4-5個鐘"},{"pid":"81af46e863d657df68bd84d3b16a084d65bcb1dc","tid":253962,"uid":33465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T01:10:57.000Z","msg":"唔掂，嗰plan太趕。到到都係到此一遊。拉鬆啲啦。建議santorini 可留耐啲"},{"pid":"368a4342ae65a65296f5d7c8e198704502ec9337","tid":253962,"uid":108029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T01:19:21.000Z","msg":"唔好坐船去聖托里尼，又要天未光就起身，又坐得耐，比少少錢坐內陸機去。"},{"pid":"bb416781ea3c4ee2ff08e1f900d4906141234aa4","tid":253962,"uid":87158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T02:04:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Meteroa要即日來回一定要坐火車<br />\n但前提佢無罷工<br />\n<br />\n另外個plan唔係唔得<br />\n不過就有啲趕頭趕命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果雅典只留一日，meteora留兩日會唔會比較好？<br />\n還是不去Iraklion，雅典留兩日,meteora留兩日，一日去Mystra。之後其餘時間留係santorini <br />\n<br />\nMeteora住宅方面其實貴唔貴？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb500069b16fa01fdecd49c7f668020192c87ca6","tid":253962,"uid":34525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T02:07:14.000Z","msg":"幫推 六月去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b964c4ef2b544a8a7b11f87f7b389b51af80028b","tid":253962,"uid":107417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T02:19:11.000Z","msg":"btw<br />\n一個男仔去希臘，應該係去Mykonos Partying. 去乜鬼Santorini呢啲浪漫地點丫。"},{"pid":"ee49f11c565a4f23020b1ba51a685147dbd05bea","tid":253962,"uid":74002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T05:13:33.000Z","msg":"下星期去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 會飛埋過塞浦路斯<br />\n去到話你知物價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd3889f220bc519cdc79054caa8bef99eeddd418","tid":253962,"uid":47565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T05:56:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Meteroa要即日來回一定要坐火車<br />\n但前提佢無罷工<br />\n<br />\n另外個plan唔係唔得<br />\n不過就有啲趕頭趕命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果雅典只留一日，meteora留兩日會唔會比較好？<br />\n還是不去Iraklion，雅典留兩日,meteora留兩日，一日去Mystra。之後其餘時間留係santorini <br />\n<br />\nMeteora住宅方面其實貴唔貴？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔去iraklion同mystra喇<br />\n兩日雅典兩日meteroa加三日santorini仲好<br />\nMeteroa廿幾歐度可以有露台望山境好似係（我覺得幾貴）<br />\n<br />\nMeteroa我去個陣火車罷工<br />\n我搭巴士都搭左6個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b28d0ed3168f0d69963d1657d63b9a2f9694ae47","tid":253962,"uid":40839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T05:58:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>btw<br />\n一個男仔去希臘，應該係去Mykonos Partying. 去乜鬼Santorini呢啲浪漫地點丫。</blockquote><br />\n去曬Mykonos同santorini啦<br />\n一支公留過係santorini幾日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d66ac99414aeab046f40189821005b7b0f8d7d35","tid":253962,"uid":87158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T19:47:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>btw<br />\n一個男仔去希臘，應該係去Mykonos Partying. 去乜鬼Santorini呢啲浪漫地點丫。</blockquote><br />\n去曬Mykonos同santorini啦<br />\n一支公留過係santorini幾日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n另外想問，坐俄羅斯航空去希臘會唔會有咩大問題？因為夠平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"637d3331de51afd89db45872bcd87070b663f555","tid":253962,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T20:45:22.000Z","msg":"Meteroa我係thessinkoi （類似咁串啦希臘第2大城市）去<br />\n之後去到好趕 自己一個包左架的士上去睇左兩個修道院 睇左一、二個鐘就落返山<br />\n之後再搭火車去athens delay左兩個鐘<br />\n搞到我自己一個半夜去到Athens<br />\n有個希臘呀叔撩我去開房 又跟住我<br />\n我跟住一對情侶先冇事<br />\n<br />\nAthens其實都係d頹垣敗瓦，我自己覺得睇衛城就夠"}]}